<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{شِيَعًا}</span> ... طَوَائِفَ مُتَفَرِّقَةً.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{نَّمُنَّ}</span> ... نَتَفَضَّلَ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْيَمِّ}</span> ... النَّهْرِ، وَهُوَ نَهْرُ النِّيلِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{خَاطِئِينَ}</span> ... آثِمِينَ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{قُرَّتُ عَيْنٍ لِّي}</span> ... مَصْدَرُ سُرُورٍ لِي.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَارِغًا}</span> ... خَالِيًا مِنْ كُلِّ شَيْءٍ إِلَّا هَمَّ مُوسَى - عليه السلام -.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَتُبْدِي بِهِ}</span> ... فَتُصَرِّحُ بِأَنَّهُ ابْنُهَا.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(١١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{قُصِّيهِ}</span> ... تَتَبَّعِي أَثَرَهُ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(١١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{عَن جُنُبٍ}</span> ... عَنْ بُعْدٍ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(١٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَكْفُلُونَهُ لَكُمْ}</span> ... يَقُومُونَ بِتَرْبِيَتِهِ وَإِرْضَاعِهِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(١٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بَلَغَ أَشُدَّهُ}</span> ... قَوِيَ بَدَنُهُ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(١٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَاسْتَوَى}</span> ... تَكَامَلَ عَقْلُهُ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(١٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مِن شِيعَتِهِ}</span> ... مِنْ قَوْمِ مُوسَى - عليه السلام -، وَهُمْ بَنُو إِسْرَائِيلَ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>